{"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".appStorage"},{"type":"text","text":" strategy used with "},{"code":"@Shared","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" now uses key-value observing instead of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NotificationCenter"},{"text":" when possible. Learn how this may affect your code.","type":"text"}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.19","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.18","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.17.1","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.17","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.15","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.14","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.13","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.12","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.11","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.10","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.9","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.8","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.7","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.6","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.5","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.4"],"generated":true}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigrationGuides"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.16","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/composablearchitecture\/migratingto1.16"]}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Article","role":"article","title":"Migrating to 1.16","modules":[{"name":"ComposableArchitecture"}]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Overview","level":2,"anchor":"Overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"There are no steps needed to migrate to 1.16 of the Composable Architecture, but there has been","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"a change to the underlying behavior of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".appStorage"},{"type":"text","text":" that one should be aware of. When using"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":".appStorage","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@Shared"},{"type":"text","text":", if your key does not contain the characters “.” or “@”, then changes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to that key in "},{"code":"UserDefaults","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" will be observed using key-value observing (KVO).","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Otherwise, "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NotificationCenter"},{"text":" will be used to observe changes.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"KVO is a far more efficient way of observing changes to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UserDefaults"},{"type":"text","text":" and it works cross-process,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as from widgets and app extensions. However, KVO does not work when the keys contain “.”"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or “@”, and so in those cases we must use the cruder tool of "},{"code":"NotificationCenter","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". That is not"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as efficient, and it forces us to perform a thread-hop when the notification is posted before"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"we can update the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@Shared"},{"text":" value. For this reason it is not possible to animate changes that are","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"made directly to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UserDefaults"},{"type":"text","text":":"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["withAnimation {","  \/\/ ⚠️ This will not animate any SwiftUI views using '@Shared(.appStorage(\"co.pointfree.count\"))'","  UserDefaults.standard.set(0, forKey: \"co.pointfree.count\")","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In general, we recommend using other delimeters for your keys, such as “\/”, “:”, “-”, etc.:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["@Shared(.appStorage(\"co:pointfree:count\")) var count = 0"],"syntax":"swift"}]}],"kind":"article","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"references":{"doc://ComposableArchitecture/documentation/ComposableArchitecture/MigratingTo1.9":{"title":"Migrating to 1.9","role":"article","kind":"article","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/composablearchitecture\/migratingto1.9","identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.9","abstract":[{"text":"Update your code to make use of the new ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"TestStore\/send(_:assert:fileID:file:line:column:)-8877x"},{"text":"","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"method on ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/TestStore"},{"type":"text","text":" which gives a succinct syntax for sending actions with case key paths, and"},{"type"